summary:
Character will chop wood until he is interrupted. Feel free to go eat or sleep while you leave him/her cutting wood. Value of the wood has not been changed. (Same old rate of pay)
* *  see also: Indefinite Mining
descriptionHtml:
Character will chop wood until he is interrupted. Feel free to go eat or sleep while you leave him/her cutting wood. Value of the wood has not been changed. (Same old rate of pay)
  I won\'t be including a cheat version of this mod (higher rate of pay) but, if you MUST have one, here is what you need to do...
  In the Creation Kit (hopefully you have it) navigate to Miscellaneous/Global and edit the \"JobsWoodValue\" there is only oe value to be changed and it is the amount you are paid for each piece of firewood. It affects only the job version of wood selling. It will not affect firewood price for other vendors.
author: TheONLYPantha
